       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. LATEFEE2.
      * LATE CHARGE ON OUTSTANDING AFTER DUE DATE (3-DAY GRACE)
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-OUTSTANDING            PIC 9(9)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-DAYS-PAST-DUE          PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-CHARGE                 PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-OUTSTANDING
           ACCEPT WS-DAYS-PAST-DUE
           PERFORM 2000-FEE
           DISPLAY 'CHARGE: ' WS-CHARGE
           STOP RUN.
       2000-FEE.
           IF WS-DAYS-PAST-DUE > 3
              COMPUTE WS-CHARGE ROUNDED = .025 * WS-OUTSTANDING
           ELSE
              MOVE ZERO TO WS-CHARGE
           END-IF.
